      <data key="d17">Shows in vivo that DNA-loop-extruding SMC complexes can traverse one another, helping explain chromosome organization with many simultaneous extruders.</data>
      <data key="d18">Shows in vivo that DNA-loop-extruding SMC complexes can traverse one another, helping explain chromosome organization with many simultaneous extruders.</data>
